{"tid":1659282,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯: 陳淑莊好了嗎？","createTime":"2019-10-17T01:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T04:19:33.000Z","uid":74778,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"974a7188886357d17b1efa28a927b2c7323707a8","tid":1659282,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:01:40.000Z","msg":"陳淑莊好了嗎？<br />\n<br />\n今天陳淑莊表現得龍精虎猛兼好勇鬥狠！有人問可以DQ佢的議員資格嗎？<br />\n<br />\n根據現時法例，任何議員倘被判入獄，連續超過三個月而未能出席會議者，他的議員身份可以被立法會主席取消；又或者，在得到立法會全體議員的三分之二票數通過後，其議員資格會被取消。<br />\n<br />\n不取消陳淑莊議員資格的原因是，她被判入獄八個月，緩刑兩年。因此她仍然可出席會議，除非建制派取得47票去DQ她，但我們現在只有43票，還欠4票。至於邵家臻情況也是相若。雖然他入獄四個月，期間立法會休會，他僥倖地避免了連續缺席三個月，他現在刑滿能夠及時出席立法會復會後的會議。<br />\n<br />\n明顯地陳淑莊已囘復健康，有見她今天如此精神的表現，我已正式向SJ提出要求她盡快向法庭提出申請覆檢陳的個案，取消她的緩刑，立即送她入獄服刑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3rey5Jf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3rey5Jf.jpg&h=bedd02cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/114759088616955/posts/2532014523558054?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F114759088616955%2Fposts%2F2532014523558054%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgMTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=5cb82d1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/114759088616955/posts/2532014523558054?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c6157a08dd720ad55b80dd62b16c92d0a5b3a6","tid":1659282,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"8cebb6f4be35d03ed95b20d271b22c107198741e","tid":1659282,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T01:06:57.000Z","msg":"親中共的大的專業資格真假難分<br />\n建議開post調查"},{"pid":"2304c6f76ea7dec8fdc193250b95489ffdb315ce","tid":1659